<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.7.13">
<l>vaṇṇa māmaṇic cōtiyai yamarar talaimakaṉaik</l>
<l>kaṇṇaṉai neṭumālait teṉkuru kūrccaṭa kōpaṉ</l>
<l>paṇṇiya tamiḻmālai yāyirattu ḷivaipaṉ ṉiraṇṭum</l>
<l>paṇṇil paṉṉiru nāmapāṭ ṭaṇṇaṟā ḷaṇaivikkumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The song of twelve names in service</l>
<l>with these twelve among the thousand in the Tamil garland prepared</l>
<l>by Caṭakōpaṉ from southern Kurukūr on Neṭumāl, Kṛṣṇa,</l>
<l>the head man of the immortals, the coloured dark sapphire light,</l>
	<l>will bring one close to the majesty’s feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
